      "datasource": {"type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093"},
      "options": {
        "flowchartData": "graph TB\n    codex[(\"🔍 Codex Hunters<br/>PERCEPTION\")]\n    memory[(\"🧠 Memory Orders<br/>MEMORY\")]\n    vault[(\"🏛️ Vault Keepers<br/>MEMORY\")]\n    pattern[(\"🕸️ Pattern Weavers<br/>REASON\")]\n    neural[(\"⚡ Neural Engine<br/>REASON\")]\n    babel[(\"🌐 Babel Gardens<br/>DISCOURSE\")]\n    orthodoxy[(\"⚖️ Orthodoxy Wardens<br/>TRUTH\")]\n    \n    codex -->|discovery| memory\n    codex -->|storage| vault\n    memory -->|analysis| pattern\n    memory -->|enrichment| neural\n    memory -->|context| babel\n    vault -->|archive| orthodoxy\n    vault -->|snapshot| memory\n    pattern -->|pattern| babel\n    pattern -->|anomaly| orthodoxy\n    neural -->|screening| babel\n    neural -->|ranking| memory\n    babel -->|narrative| orthodoxy\n    babel -->|translation| memory\n    orthodoxy -->|validation| memory\n    orthodoxy -->|audit| codex\n    \n    classDef perception fill:#3498db,stroke:#2980b9,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff\n    classDef memory fill:#9b59b6,stroke:#8e44ad,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff\n    classDef reason fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#c0392b,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff\n    classDef discourse fill:#f39c12,stroke:#e67e22,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff\n    classDef truth fill:#27ae60,stroke:#229954,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff\n    \n    class codex perception\n    class memory,vault memory\n    class pattern,neural reason\n    class babel discourse\n    class orthodoxy truth",
        "mermaidRender": true,
        "center": true,
        "scale": "100%",
        "lock": false,
        "grid": false,
        "bgColor": "#1a1a1a",
        "tooltip": true
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "mappings": [
            {
              "type": "range",
              "options": {
                "from": 0,
                "to": 3000,
                "result": {"color": "green"}
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "range",
              "options": {
                "from": 3000,
                "to": 5000,
                "result": {"color": "yellow"}
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "range",
              "options": {
                "from": 5000,
                "to": 10000,
                "result": {"color": "red"}
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sacred_order_activity{sacred_order=\"memory\"}",
